name: Passport Photo
description: Photo Basics ::: Submit a color photo, taken in last 6 months :: Use a clear image of your face. Do not use filters commonly used on social media. Have someone else take your photo. No selfies. Take off your eyeglasses for your photo. Use a plain white or off-white background :: Resolution, Print Size, and Quality :: Submit a high resolution photo that is not blurry, grainy, or pixelated. The correct size of a passport photo is: 2 x 2 inches (51 x 51 mm) Head must be between 1 -1 3/8 inches (25 - 35 mm) from the bottom of the chin to the top of the head :: Printed on matte or glossy photo quality paper Do not digitally change the photo
